    <description>SAP Banking Services (Generic Market Data) 400, 450, and 500 does not perform necessary authorization checks for an authenticated user, resulting in escalation of privileges. An unauthorized User is allowed to display restricted Business Partner Generic Market Data (GMD), due to improper authorization check.</description>
    <dc:date>2021-01-12T15:15:16Z</dc:date>
  </item>
  <item rdf:about="https://web.nvd.nist.gov/view/vuln/detail?vulnId=CVE-2021-21468">
